Sell Galaxy S6

Want to sell an Galaxy S6? You’ve come to the right place

The Samsung Galaxy S6 & S6 Edge phones were launched at Mobile World Congress on 1st March 2015 to rave reviews from the industry. Customers have always loved the powerful technology and functionality of the Samsung Galaxy range but were not as keen on the plastic backs. The S6 & S6 Edge changed all this by sporting a new all aluminium frame that gave it a much more premium look and feel. The S6 Edge in particular was very ground-breaking as it was the first smartphone with a curved screen. This high-end spec means that the S6 Edge holds its value well and achieves a high re-sale value.
